### Test trends endpoint with 30 days period (explicit)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test trends endpoint with 90 days period
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=90
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test trends endpoint with 365 days period
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=365
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test trends endpoint with invalid period (should return validation error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=invalid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test trends endpoint without authentication (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends

### Test trends endpoint with officer role (should only see assigned reports)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=30
Authorization: Bearer officer-token-here